 Joan Collins, 89, was featured in an Instagram post by Sir Rod Stewart’s ex-wife, Alana, 77, as she stumbled upon a throwback photo. The star-studded snap was from a 1987 New Year’s Eve party at Alana’s home. Alongside Joan was her daughter Katy and stepson Robert as well as the late Burt Bacharach and his ex-wife Carole Bayer Sager. Alana shared the snap with her 99,000 followers, writing in the caption: “Where does the time go?” The 89-year-old Hollywood veteran looked every bit the star then and now, with fans quick to point out one particularly fabulous aspect of the 1987 star.